<plot>Rebecca, after working late at her babysitting job, decides to take a short cut home through an alleyway. In the shadows she sees a scary man and thinks she may have made a mistake. Too late to turn back she turns to prayer for God to protect her through the Alleyway. Here we ask a very important question, "When it gets dark, who is walking you home?"</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?031912</url></doc>
